2
00:00:25,160 --> 00:00:30,459
♫  Happily tossing and turning in the spring and autumn  ♫

3
00:00:30,459 --> 00:00:34,980
♫  Nothing but love and freedom  ♫

4
00:00:34,980 --> 00:00:41,099
♫  Over thorny roads, across treacherous heights  ♫

5
00:00:41,099 --> 00:00:47,879
♫  After a thousand sails have passed, who will swim with you  ♫

6
00:00:47,879 --> 00:00:53,159
♫  I'm willing to go through the ups and downs of the world for the sake of the people  ♫

7
00:00:53,159 --> 00:00:58,259
♫  Still embracing the original innocence  ♫

8
00:00:58,259 --> 00:01:03,479
♫  The sound of vows falling to the ground, 
 this heart can be proved by Heaven and Earth  ♫

9
00:01:03,479 --> 00:01:08,579
♫  The darker it is the more dazzling like stars there are  ♫

10
00:01:08,580 --> 00:01:13,579
♫  I wish to stride through the ups and downs of fate, and live towards the sun  ♫

11
00:01:13,579 --> 00:01:18,539
♫  Moments turn into eternity, fleeting years become forever  ♫

12
00:01:18,539 --> 00:01:24,000
♫  The road ahead is long, 
 and there is an unquenchable light in my heart  ♫

13
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:29,239
♫  Because someone is waiting for me  ♫

14
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:36,918
♫  There is one person who will complete the dream  ♫

15
00:01:36,919 --> 00:01:39,019
   

16
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:43,059
   

17
00:01:43,059 --> 00:01:44,939
   

18
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:48,040
   

19
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:57,100
Here we have the noblest lady of Jiangzuo.

20
00:01:57,719 --> 00:02:01,440
What would others think of you if they were to figure out

21
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:03,759
the cheap ploys you've resorted to?

22
00:02:03,759 --> 00:02:05,159
I did nothing.

23
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:07,180
It has nothing to do with me.

24
00:02:07,180 --> 00:02:12,420
Miss Sun, I need to tell you that I know the tea tasted strange.

25
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:16,218
I didn't expose you because I found it pointless.

26
00:02:16,218 --> 00:02:20,600
However, you're getting under my skin by doing so several times.

27
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:26,998
Lord Ding and I go way back to our childhood.

28
00:02:26,999 --> 00:02:31,880
But when I finally returned to the capital, everything changed totally.

29
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,580
You're in my way!

30
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:38,619
Miss Sun, let me repeat this to you.

31
00:02:38,619 --> 00:02:41,100
Before this, I didn't hold you accountable

32
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:45,560
because I'd taken your jealousy lightly as it wouldn't affect to much.

33
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:47,558
But you keep making mischief

34
00:02:47,558 --> 00:02:49,958
and have affected the operation of the Ministry of Revenue.

35
00:02:49,958 --> 00:02:52,500
Don't blame me for turning against you!

36
00:02:55,519 --> 00:02:57,439
All right, Official Mu.

37
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:59,320
I promise it won't happen again.

38
00:03:01,359 --> 00:03:04,059
You're here, Your Majesty.

39
00:03:05,759 --> 00:03:07,839
- Greetings, Your Majesty. 
 - Greetings, Your Majesty.

40
00:03:14,659 --> 00:03:18,959
I suppose Miss Sun might be having some difficulties after arriving here.

41
00:03:18,959 --> 00:03:22,458
Besides, she has to do her duty at the Ministry of Revenue.

42
00:03:22,458 --> 00:03:25,539
So, I came to check on her.

43
00:03:25,539 --> 00:03:31,239
And now I run into you here, who's bullying a newcomer.

44
00:03:33,399 --> 00:03:35,399
Official Mu,

45
00:03:35,399 --> 00:03:39,240
do you admit your fault?

46
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:42,918
 They're really meant to be in one family. Sheesh. 

47
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:45,660
I do.

48
00:03:47,980 --> 00:03:54,619
I lost control of myself and snapped at Observer Sun just now.

49
00:04:00,499 --> 00:04:03,120
My Lord, bad news.

50
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,859
While the Dowager Empress was on her way to visit Observer Sun,

51
00:04:04,859 --> 00:04:07,539
she caught Official Mu and Observer Sun having a spat.

52
00:04:07,539 --> 00:04:10,320
Hence, Official Mu was punished by kneeling for two hours.

53
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:13,939
- How long has it been? 
 - More than an hour.

54
00:04:15,459 --> 00:04:18,158
- Bring along the anti-swelling ointment. 
 - Yes.

55
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:29,238
Sir, you can send this letter to your family.

56
00:04:29,238 --> 00:04:31,519
I've written everything you wanted me to write.

57
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:34,499
All right. Thank you, Young Master.

58
00:04:35,659 --> 00:04:37,459
Thank you so much.

59
00:04:51,540 --> 00:04:55,119
Man'er told me you came to Jishan Hall as soon as you got off work.

60
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:57,740
You've skipped dinner, too.

61
00:04:59,539 --> 00:05:01,239
What's this?

62
00:05:03,060 --> 00:05:06,720
Man'er said you like sweet desserts.

63
00:05:08,879 --> 00:05:10,579
Have a seat.

64
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:44,899
Princess Roujia, you're here too.

65
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:47,379
Jishan Hall belongs to Her Highness.

66
00:05:47,379 --> 00:05:49,700
Naturally, she's here.

67
00:05:50,459 --> 00:05:52,558
Well. Anyway, I'm here for you.

68
00:05:52,559 --> 00:05:54,459
Me?

69
00:05:54,459 --> 00:05:57,458
You... You want to talk to Official Shen?

70
00:05:57,458 --> 00:05:58,878
Yes, I do.

71
00:05:58,879 --> 00:06:01,458
Shen Jinghong promised to teach me poems of the Central Plains.

72
00:06:01,458 --> 00:06:03,078
But he's too busy.

73
00:06:03,079 --> 00:06:05,219
So I came here myself.

74
00:06:06,459 --> 00:06:09,160
Great effort, Official Shen.

75
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:12,979
I don't mind lending the place to you.

76
00:06:16,339 --> 00:06:20,820
Men from the Central Plains stick to promises, don't they?

77
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:25,619
It's time for you to fulfill your promise.

78
00:06:41,700 --> 00:06:47,679
The Dowager Empress wants you to kneel for two full hours, not a second less.

79
00:06:54,239 --> 00:06:56,039
Official Mu,

80
00:06:56,039 --> 00:06:59,580
my family is the most prestigious clan in Jiangzuo,

81
00:06:59,580 --> 00:07:03,659
while I'm the legitimate eldest daughter of the Sun clan.

82
00:07:05,559 --> 00:07:08,720
Behind me, it's the Dowager Empress and Consort Shu.

83
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:14,579
If I marry Lord Ding, we're a fated couple for his promising future.

84
00:07:14,579 --> 00:07:16,040
While you,

85
00:07:17,779 --> 00:07:18,819
no way.

86
00:07:18,819 --> 00:07:20,699
Stop your pipe dream.

87
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:31,639
Frankly, it's unnecessary to corner me like this

88
00:07:31,639 --> 00:07:35,259
and spend so much time and effort on me.

89
00:07:36,479 --> 00:07:38,479
He doesn't like you.

90
00:07:38,479 --> 00:07:40,520
It's not that I don't like you.

91
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:43,279
But you keep showing up before me every day.

92
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:47,659
I almost started to believe that you admired me instead.

93
00:07:50,419 --> 00:07:53,659
Is it worth the effort?

94
00:07:55,779 --> 00:07:59,320
If you leave, at least...

95
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:01,779
At least he'll be conscious of me.

96
00:08:03,940 --> 00:08:07,540
Miss Sun, let me repeat this to you.

97
00:08:07,540 --> 00:08:09,719
He is himself, and I am myself.

98
00:08:09,719 --> 00:08:13,680
Whomever he chooses to marry has nothing to do with me.

99
00:08:35,780 --> 00:08:38,380
His Lordship said not to reveal his name.

100
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:39,798
- Understood. 
 - Thank you.

101
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:40,799
Thank you.

102
00:09:02,059 --> 00:09:03,659
Official Li.

103
00:09:06,260 --> 00:09:09,980
I heard that you were punished by the Dowager Empress.

104
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:17,999
Oh, dear.

105
00:09:17,999 --> 00:09:20,459
You shouldn't have acted impulsively.

106
00:09:20,459 --> 00:09:22,259
Miss Sun is from a noble family.

107
00:09:22,259 --> 00:09:25,739
There's no way you can get the upper hand when you confront her.

108
00:09:26,380 --> 00:09:28,420
Apply the ointment now.

109
00:09:28,420 --> 00:09:31,120
It helps to get the swelling down.

110
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:33,959
I always use this. It's effective.

111
00:09:38,579 --> 00:09:42,820
Thank you for sharing this ointment with me.

112
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:45,778
I'll just use a little bit and return the rest to you.

113
00:09:45,778 --> 00:09:48,319
No. Keep it.

114
00:09:48,319 --> 00:09:49,879
I have a lot more.

115
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:52,980
If so, thank you so much.

116
00:09:52,980 --> 00:09:55,160
Don't mention it.

117
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:22,579
Which one do you think has hurt him?

118
00:10:24,919 --> 00:10:29,599
"Whomever he chooses to marry has nothing to do with me."

119
00:10:30,819 --> 00:10:32,660
Oh, that hurts.

120
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,798
My Lord.

121
00:10:42,799 --> 00:10:45,159
Why did you ask for me?

122
00:10:46,260 --> 00:10:50,320
From now on, send someone else to deliver the documents.

123
00:10:57,785 --> 00:10:59,139
   

124
00:10:59,139 --> 00:11:00,840
 Are you all busy? 

125
00:11:03,159 --> 00:11:06,400
It's an urgent document.

126
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:09,020
I'll deliver this, Official Li.

127
00:11:14,460 --> 00:11:17,560
We shall give Observer Sun a chance.

128
00:11:39,179 --> 00:11:40,958
Official Li.

129
00:11:40,959 --> 00:11:42,239
- Me again? 
 - Yes.

130
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,158
Yes.

131
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:44,159
Go ahead.

132
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:58,240
What's going on?

133
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:00,760
It used to be me, though.

134
00:12:10,159 --> 00:12:11,319
Official Li.

135
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:14,020
Do you need me to deliver an urgent document?

136
00:12:14,020 --> 00:12:15,339
You've been helping a lot, Observer Sun.

137
00:12:15,339 --> 00:12:17,160
Not at all.

138
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:29,320
My Lord.

139
00:12:30,220 --> 00:12:32,939
It's scorching. Let me hold an umbrella for you.

140
00:12:32,939 --> 00:12:34,640
My Lord.

141
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:46,938
Are you all right?

142
00:12:46,938 --> 00:12:48,439
Thank you.

143
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:54,260
Greetings, My Lord.

144
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:05,240
My Lord.

145
00:13:07,579 --> 00:13:09,880
Do not get heatstroke.

146
00:13:14,040 --> 00:13:15,740
Thank you.

147
00:13:26,220 --> 00:13:28,040
   

148
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:30,458
Young Lady. Young Lady.

149
00:13:30,458 --> 00:13:34,299
Young Lady, what happened?

150
00:13:35,399 --> 00:13:39,678
Nothing. I think I got tired from walking.

151
00:13:42,639 --> 00:13:46,479
Young Lady, look at this.

152
00:13:50,539 --> 00:13:52,858
- Spider. 
 - It's an auspicious spider.

153
00:13:52,858 --> 00:13:54,979
Young Lady, the Qiqiao Festival is around the corner.

154
00:13:54,979 --> 00:13:56,680
Do you remember that?

155
00:13:57,399 --> 00:13:58,878
No.

156
00:13:58,879 --> 00:14:01,718
It's fine. I've saved the date.

157
00:14:01,718 --> 00:14:05,038
Put this in a new chest tomorrow and check it the next morning.

158
00:14:05,039 --> 00:14:07,679
The denser the spider web, the higher your chances of standing out.

159
00:14:08,639 --> 00:14:09,939
Oh, right.

160
00:14:15,899 --> 00:14:17,499
Look at this.

161
00:14:18,140 --> 00:14:20,420
This is Qiaoguo. 
  (Sweet and crispy pastry) 

162
00:14:22,299 --> 00:14:24,499
I can't see why I should celebrate this.

163
00:14:24,499 --> 00:14:26,939
I don't want to celebrate the Qiqiao Festival.

164
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:29,400
What has happened? Why not?

165
00:14:29,400 --> 00:14:32,400
We can have yummy food and lots of fun during the Qiqiao Festival.

166
00:14:35,879 --> 00:14:38,040
Juli, let me ask you this.

167
00:14:38,040 --> 00:14:43,020
Zhimo has been giving you grapes and pastries.

168
00:14:43,020 --> 00:14:48,780
But if he suddenly gives them to another person one day, would you be upset?

169
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:55,660
I won't if he gives them to Zhijian.

170
00:14:55,660 --> 00:15:00,299
 I used to think that I wouldn't feel hurt when he dated any women. 

171
00:15:00,299 --> 00:15:03,240
 But it seems that it's not the case. 

172
00:15:04,339 --> 00:15:06,920
 Do not get heatstroke. 

173
00:15:09,860 --> 00:15:11,560
 Thank you. 

174
00:15:16,899 --> 00:15:22,099
Young Lady, are you feeling unwell?

175
00:15:25,779 --> 00:15:27,279
I'm fine.

176
00:15:32,579 --> 00:15:34,339
Something came up, Official Mu.

177
00:15:34,339 --> 00:15:35,940
Next door. Hurry.

178
00:15:36,920 --> 00:15:37,950
All right.

179
00:15:37,950 --> 00:15:39,880
   

180
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:43,440
My Lord.

181
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:45,539
- My Lord. 
 - Official Mu.  
 - Imperial Physician Lu.

182
00:15:45,539 --> 00:15:48,378
His condition is bad. We need your help.

183
00:15:50,779 --> 00:15:52,820
Why did he relapse all of a sudden?

184
00:15:53,699 --> 00:15:58,279
The acupuncture therapy can only extend his life.

185
00:15:58,279 --> 00:16:02,179
If his sickness were to recurrently relapse, even if he didn't die,

186
00:16:02,179 --> 00:16:05,759
he'd become foolish after waking up.

187
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:12,219
Acupuncture therapy won't help much without the Snow Dust Pill.

188
00:16:12,219 --> 00:16:14,180
What should we do now?

189
00:16:14,180 --> 00:16:16,379
Let's try again, Official Mu.

190
00:16:16,379 --> 00:16:17,680
All right.

191
00:16:19,660 --> 00:16:21,660
Thank you, Official Mu.

192
00:16:24,579 --> 00:16:26,479
It's my duty.

193
00:16:39,639 --> 00:16:42,179
Your Highness, the lecture is over.

194
00:16:45,059 --> 00:16:46,759
Official Mu.

195
00:16:46,759 --> 00:16:48,379
Yes, Your Highness.

196
00:16:49,260 --> 00:16:52,359
As the adage goes, "Develop a counterattack plan before riots erupt;

197
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:54,259
Stabilize the nation before crises emerge."

198
00:16:54,259 --> 00:16:58,078
But what should we do if someone conceals the truth from both superiors and subordinates?

199
00:16:58,078 --> 00:16:59,439
Second Brother.

200
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:01,759
Have you heard the news?

201
00:17:01,759 --> 00:17:05,400
Today, Grandmother arranged a marriage between Lord Ding and Yunyun.

202
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:08,398
Yunyun has loved Uncle for seven years

203
00:17:08,399 --> 00:17:11,179
and refuses to get engaged to any men at her marriageable age.

204
00:17:11,179 --> 00:17:16,120
Maybe Grandmother grants her wish concerning her deep affection.

205
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:21,739
Regarding your question about the adage,

206
00:17:21,739 --> 00:17:25,759
I'll explain it to you precisely in the next lecture.

207
00:17:25,759 --> 00:17:26,778
Sure.

208
00:17:26,778 --> 00:17:28,479
I shall take my leave.

209
00:17:30,885 --> 00:17:33,319
   

210
00:17:33,319 --> 00:17:34,620
 Your Highness. 

211
00:17:35,439 --> 00:17:38,799
You called me here on short notice. Is it something urgent?

212
00:17:40,439 --> 00:17:43,180
Jinghong, take a seat.

213
00:18:00,679 --> 00:18:02,779
Jinghong,

214
00:18:02,779 --> 00:18:06,900
you're close to Official Mu, aren't you?

215
00:18:08,059 --> 00:18:09,559
Yes.

216
00:18:09,559 --> 00:18:13,160
Do you know what her hobby is?

217
00:18:15,220 --> 00:18:19,399
Your Highness, why don't you ask her in person?

218
00:18:26,280 --> 00:18:27,780
Here's the thing.

219
00:18:29,879 --> 00:18:35,779
Previously, I offended her, and I feel terrible about that.

220
00:18:35,779 --> 00:18:39,600
I'm waiting for a chance to apologize to her.

221
00:18:40,539 --> 00:18:42,959
So, what's her hobby?

222
00:18:46,919 --> 00:18:49,179
Well, Official Mu...

223
00:18:53,260 --> 00:18:54,660
Money.

224
00:18:59,139 --> 00:19:01,758
Anything else besides money?

225
00:19:01,758 --> 00:19:04,920
Apart from money, there is none.

226
00:19:08,220 --> 00:19:11,558
Forget it. I'll figure this out myself.

227
00:19:25,759 --> 00:19:27,020
 Have you heard the news? 

228
00:19:27,020 --> 00:19:30,859
 Today, Grandmother arranged a marriage between Lord Ding and Yunyun. 

229
00:19:36,199 --> 00:19:37,799
 Do you want one? 

230
00:19:43,679 --> 00:19:46,700
Young Lady, you're back.

231
00:19:46,700 --> 00:19:49,559
Juli, why are you so well dressed today?

232
00:19:49,559 --> 00:19:51,058
Oh, Young Lady.

233
00:19:51,058 --> 00:19:54,079
Did you forget that? Today is the Qiqiao Festival.

234
00:19:54,079 --> 00:19:55,520
I see.

235
00:19:55,520 --> 00:19:59,619
No wonder the streets have been decorated.

236
00:19:59,619 --> 00:20:01,979
I received a bag of Qiaoguo during lunch.

237
00:20:01,979 --> 00:20:04,159
Young Lady, you should dress up, too.

238
00:20:04,159 --> 00:20:05,979
We're hanging out later.

239
00:20:05,979 --> 00:20:07,560
- Come on. 
 - Juli, I'm not going.

240
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:10,579
I'm not in the mood for that.

241
00:20:11,180 --> 00:20:12,739
No, please. Young Lady.

242
00:20:12,739 --> 00:20:14,478
It's only held once a year.

243
00:20:14,479 --> 00:20:16,238
You should enjoy yourself.

244
00:20:16,239 --> 00:20:18,938
Come on. Go and get ready.

245
00:20:18,938 --> 00:20:20,259
No, Juli.

246
00:20:20,259 --> 00:20:22,599
Hurry up, Young Lady.

247
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:26,239
There are so many sky lanterns.

248
00:20:26,239 --> 00:20:27,819
It's crowded here.

249
00:20:27,819 --> 00:20:30,199
Juli, look over there.

250
00:20:30,199 --> 00:20:32,060
And there.

251
00:20:49,239 --> 00:20:50,539
Look.

252
00:20:59,360 --> 00:21:00,638
This is amazing.

253
00:21:00,638 --> 00:21:02,939
- How did he manage that?  
 -  I have no idea.

254
00:21:04,260 --> 00:21:06,239
Come on, let's go over there.

255
00:21:34,879 --> 00:21:36,479
Out of my way.

256
00:21:37,199 --> 00:21:40,259
Uncle, look at this lantern. It's cool, isn't it?

257
00:21:40,259 --> 00:21:42,260
I solved the riddles and won it.

258
00:21:54,059 --> 00:21:56,719
Juli, go and meet up with Zhimo.

259
00:21:56,719 --> 00:21:58,479
I need to go somewhere.

260
00:21:58,479 --> 00:22:01,320
Let's meet up later, Young Lady.

261
00:22:08,840 --> 00:22:10,278
It's pretty good.

262
00:22:10,278 --> 00:22:12,720
