Nice?

267
00:22:21,580 --> 00:22:22,919
Yes.

268
00:22:22,919 --> 00:22:24,818
You never like sweet food.

269
00:22:24,818 --> 00:22:28,160
And yet you lie to please the girl.

270
00:22:29,159 --> 00:22:30,238
Zhijian.

271
00:22:30,239 --> 00:22:32,079
Do you want to join us for the festival?

272
00:22:32,079 --> 00:22:33,958
I don't celebrate the Qiqiao Festival.

273
00:22:33,958 --> 00:22:35,799
What festival do you celebrate?

274
00:22:35,799 --> 00:22:37,799
I celebrate the Ghost Festival.

275
00:22:39,299 --> 00:22:40,499
Ignore him.

276
00:22:40,499 --> 00:22:42,478
Wait for me, Official Shen!

277
00:22:42,478 --> 00:22:44,079
You...

278
00:22:44,079 --> 00:22:45,359
Princess Jing'an.

279
00:22:45,360 --> 00:22:47,680
What is it again?

280
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:51,779
I was told that people in the Central Plains celebrate the Qiqiao Festival today.

281
00:22:51,800 --> 00:22:54,440
Many couples celebrate this.

282
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:57,999
Oh, I remember something. I have some tasks to attend to now.

283
00:22:57,999 --> 00:22:59,079
How about this?

284
00:22:59,080 --> 00:23:01,638
There will be many beautiful lanterns since it's a festival today.

285
00:23:01,639 --> 00:23:02,778
You should go and take a look around.

286
00:23:02,778 --> 00:23:05,359
- I shall take my leave. 
 - Let's... Let's go together...

287
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:07,659
Wait for me!

288
00:23:07,659 --> 00:23:10,820
   

289
00:23:17,339 --> 00:23:19,600
Since I've made up my mind,

290
00:23:20,759 --> 00:23:22,700
I shouldn't regret it.

291
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:26,119
This lantern...

292
00:23:27,139 --> 00:23:29,039
will be the proof...

293
00:23:31,320 --> 00:23:34,239
of my past liking for Lord Ding.

294
00:23:40,560 --> 00:23:43,960
"Heaven never ages; love never dies."

295
00:23:44,679 --> 00:23:47,159
Since love does exist,

296
00:23:47,159 --> 00:23:50,800
why did you give in?

297
00:23:54,919 --> 00:23:56,419
My Lord.

298
00:23:57,379 --> 00:23:59,360
You heard everything.

299
00:23:59,360 --> 00:24:02,079
I won't deny it, then.

300
00:24:05,180 --> 00:24:06,980
Yes.

301
00:24:06,980 --> 00:24:08,580
My Lord.

302
00:24:10,080 --> 00:24:12,260
I do have feelings for you.

303
00:24:16,779 --> 00:24:18,279
But...

304
00:24:18,879 --> 00:24:22,000
But after Miss Sun came,

305
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:23,720
I realized...

306
00:24:25,040 --> 00:24:27,020
that my liking...

307
00:24:28,579 --> 00:24:30,720
won't do you any good.

308
00:24:32,139 --> 00:24:37,139
Instead, Miss Sun comes from a noble origin.

309
00:24:38,280 --> 00:24:43,660
The two of you are meant for each other.

310
00:24:44,439 --> 00:24:48,239
By the way, I forgot to congratulate you.

311
00:24:49,900 --> 00:24:54,440
You're expecting a wedding with Miss Sun.

312
00:24:55,840 --> 00:24:58,120
Take your blessing back.

313
00:24:59,020 --> 00:25:01,360
I don't need it.

314
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:05,599
As you've seen,

315
00:25:05,599 --> 00:25:09,460
the Dowager Empress has been trying to set me up with Sun Yunyun.

316
00:25:10,339 --> 00:25:12,279
But I don't want to.

317
00:25:13,579 --> 00:25:18,059
No one can force me to do something I don't want.

318
00:25:19,660 --> 00:25:25,100
Likewise, no one can stop me from something I want.

319
00:25:28,239 --> 00:25:29,939
Are you saying...

320
00:25:31,779 --> 00:25:33,899
that you don't want to marry her?

321
00:25:34,980 --> 00:25:36,739
Of course, I don't.

322
00:25:36,739 --> 00:25:40,440
 Your Majesty, I know you attach great importance to my marriage. 

323
00:25:40,440 --> 00:25:45,360
 However, I hope to decide on my own marriage. 

324
00:25:46,600 --> 00:25:52,819
 Miss Sun is a good choice, but she's in a prestigious yet complicated position. 

325
00:25:52,819 --> 00:25:57,859
 I know I'm a lord, and I have no freedom to decide on my marriage. 

326
00:25:57,859 --> 00:26:01,579
 In that case, I'd rather not have it. 

327
00:26:01,579 --> 00:26:07,700
 Do you mean you're not marrying anyone in this life? 

328
00:26:11,679 --> 00:26:13,779
 Please grant my wish, Your Majesty. 

329
00:26:13,779 --> 00:26:15,380
 Miss Sun, 

330
00:26:17,539 --> 00:26:21,859
 I think you've visited the market you want. 

331
00:26:21,859 --> 00:26:26,539
 As for the rest, I have already made myself clear. 

332
00:26:26,539 --> 00:26:30,080
 I have no patience for women. 

333
00:26:30,080 --> 00:26:32,179
 You should know what I mean. 

334
00:26:32,719 --> 00:26:36,119
 Don't bring yourself disgrace before the public. 

335
00:26:36,120 --> 00:26:37,720
 My Lord. 

336
00:26:39,080 --> 00:26:45,800
 I spare no effort to walk towards you and be seen by you. 

337
00:26:45,800 --> 00:26:49,700
I've liked you for seven years.

338
00:26:52,800 --> 00:26:58,799
 But love can't be measured by time. 

339
00:27:15,159 --> 00:27:16,559
My Lord.

340
00:27:18,840 --> 00:27:22,640
Thank you for doing all this for me.

341
00:27:23,639 --> 00:27:28,139
However, I'm selfish.

342
00:27:29,120 --> 00:27:33,179
When I escaped to the capital,

343
00:27:33,179 --> 00:27:36,480
all I wanted was to make money and become an official.

344
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:41,720
I planned to use my salary to support Juli and myself until we grow old.

345
00:27:45,999 --> 00:27:50,600
I've made up my mind that I didn't want...

346
00:27:53,039 --> 00:27:56,259
to be confined to the identity of a wife

347
00:27:56,259 --> 00:27:58,899
or trapped by love.

348
00:28:03,360 --> 00:28:04,860
My Lord,

349
00:28:05,819 --> 00:28:07,700
I have my concerns.

350
00:28:08,679 --> 00:28:10,519
You know that well.

351
00:28:11,959 --> 00:28:13,659
Therefore...

352
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:18,100
I'm so sorry.

353
00:28:18,840 --> 00:28:21,020
I can't respond to you.

354
00:28:33,299 --> 00:28:34,999
I'd thought of these...

355
00:28:36,360 --> 00:28:39,279
when I was in Jiangnan.

356
00:28:40,840 --> 00:28:45,140
At that time, I made a decision.

357
00:28:49,339 --> 00:28:52,060
But I was clueless about what your plan was.

358
00:28:52,819 --> 00:28:54,219
So,

359
00:28:55,439 --> 00:28:57,779
I daren't make any move.

360
00:29:05,840 --> 00:29:08,060
Before I met you,

361
00:29:09,579 --> 00:29:14,059
my life was like a withered branch dipped in the mire.

362
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:19,840
I merely lived by the will

363
00:29:19,840 --> 00:29:21,880
to find the truth.

364
00:29:23,579 --> 00:29:27,919
I wish I could witness a peaceful and prosperous nation before I die.

365
00:29:27,919 --> 00:29:31,599
I'd never expected that I would meet someone

366
00:29:31,599 --> 00:29:36,180
I'd want to spend my life with.

367
00:29:37,400 --> 00:29:42,100
I'd once promised that I wouldn't fall in love with someone

368
00:29:42,100 --> 00:29:45,200
or marry a woman and have children with her...

369
00:29:46,479 --> 00:29:49,159
before the Emperor and the Dowager Empress.

370
00:29:54,139 --> 00:29:55,739
But it seems...

371
00:29:57,840 --> 00:30:02,840
I've broken the first promise.

372
00:30:06,080 --> 00:30:07,580
My Lord.

373
00:30:09,500 --> 00:30:11,480
How am I deserving of that?

374
00:30:13,679 --> 00:30:15,579
If my love for you...

375
00:30:17,519 --> 00:30:20,700
will force you to give up on things you like,

376
00:30:22,099 --> 00:30:24,539
then the love isn't genuine.

377
00:30:26,659 --> 00:30:30,459
Zhuohua, if you have feelings for me too,

378
00:30:32,560 --> 00:30:34,839
please allow me to accompany you.

379
00:30:36,099 --> 00:30:38,099
You don't marry anyone.

380
00:30:38,099 --> 00:30:40,060
And I won't marry anyone either.

381
00:30:44,660 --> 00:30:46,960
Let's do this for the rest of our lives.

382
00:30:48,020 --> 00:30:49,620
All right?

383
00:30:52,959 --> 00:30:57,659
We'll do this for the rest of our lives?

384
00:30:59,220 --> 00:31:05,119
Yes. Allow me to accompany you when you're pursuing your passion.

385
00:31:08,959 --> 00:31:10,999
Not all companionship...

386
00:31:12,439 --> 00:31:14,920
must be in the name of marriage.

387
00:31:15,759 --> 00:31:18,020
What do you think, Zhuohua?

388
00:31:19,220 --> 00:31:20,720
My Lord.

389
00:31:21,659 --> 00:31:23,359
Are you...

390
00:31:24,839 --> 00:31:26,920
Are you sure?

391
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:28,800
Certainly.

