00:32:41,704 --> 00:32:45,300
♫  Obviously willing to swear life and death 
 to be entangled for a lifetime  ♫

406
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:49,392
♫  For a moment of heartbeat, paying homage to Heaven  ♫

407
00:32:49,392 --> 00:32:56,019
♫  Want to have one more glimpse of you, 
 even just for a second more  ♫

408
00:32:56,019 --> 00:32:57,620
 Bravo! 

409
00:33:03,879 --> 00:33:05,279
Official Mu.

410
00:33:09,139 --> 00:33:10,739
Busted, thief!

411
00:33:13,639 --> 00:33:16,280
I'm so sorry.

412
00:33:16,280 --> 00:33:19,019
You're a girl, but you have great strength.

413
00:33:21,260 --> 00:33:23,060
Where's Official Mu?

414
00:33:23,060 --> 00:33:25,220
Young Lady?

415
00:33:25,220 --> 00:33:27,900
She's not with me.

416
00:33:27,900 --> 00:33:30,039
I don't know where she is.

417
00:33:45,039 --> 00:33:46,639
It's for you.

418
00:33:48,479 --> 00:33:49,979
What happened?

419
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:53,799
I accidentally hurt First Prince's arm just now.

420
00:33:53,799 --> 00:33:55,980
Will he hold me accountable?

421
00:33:55,980 --> 00:33:57,858
Don't worry. His Lordship will help you.

422
00:33:57,858 --> 00:33:59,359
I'll tell him about this.

423
00:33:59,359 --> 00:34:00,920
Really?

424
00:34:02,260 --> 00:34:03,960
It's sweet.

425
00:34:16,240 --> 00:34:20,100
Isn't this the broken jade pendant?

426
00:34:21,659 --> 00:34:24,039
This is your gift for the Tongxin Festival.

427
00:34:24,039 --> 00:34:26,699
Half for you, and the other half for me.

428
00:34:28,219 --> 00:34:30,680
Frankly, I prepared this long ago.

429
00:34:31,380 --> 00:34:34,260
I didn't get a suitable chance to give it to you.

430
00:34:35,799 --> 00:34:40,659
All I ask for is a soulmate despite not marrying each other.

431
00:34:46,900 --> 00:34:50,300
I'll take that as a yes.

432
00:34:59,460 --> 00:35:02,570
   

433
00:35:10,920 --> 00:35:13,059
Young Lady, your congee.

434
00:35:13,059 --> 00:35:15,339
Come on.

435
00:35:15,339 --> 00:35:16,959
Here.

436
00:35:22,359 --> 00:35:26,358
Young Lady, isn't this the jade pendant Lord Ding gave you?

437
00:35:35,579 --> 00:35:37,579
Young Lady.

438
00:35:37,579 --> 00:35:40,219
Is anything bothering you?

439
00:35:40,219 --> 00:35:43,119
No, nothing is bothering me.

440
00:35:46,820 --> 00:35:49,380
Money issues?

441
00:35:49,380 --> 00:35:52,300
You want to trade this jade pendant for money and pay for the rental?

442
00:35:53,219 --> 00:35:56,638
I know the rental in the capital is getting higher.

443
00:35:56,639 --> 00:36:00,239
Years of rent is enough to buy a house.

444
00:36:00,239 --> 00:36:03,740
Young Lady, we should consider buying our own house.

445
00:36:04,279 --> 00:36:05,618
Juli,

446
00:36:05,618 --> 00:36:07,219
look at this.

447
00:36:08,240 --> 00:36:12,399
These are the house and land deeds of this place.

448
00:36:13,460 --> 00:36:17,619
Wait... But we rent this house, don't we?

449
00:36:17,619 --> 00:36:21,618
Lord Ding gave me these deeds last night.

450
00:36:21,618 --> 00:36:24,379
He said it was a gift for me.

451
00:36:24,379 --> 00:36:25,999
Last night?

452
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:28,518
Didn't you say that you wouldn't care about Lord Ding anymore?

453
00:36:28,518 --> 00:36:30,219
Did you make up?

454
00:36:30,860 --> 00:36:34,200
Well, it's more than that.

455
00:36:34,200 --> 00:36:37,678
Whoa! Lord Ding is so generous.

456
00:36:40,340 --> 00:36:41,819
Young Lady,

457
00:36:41,819 --> 00:36:44,798
do you think Lord Ding will hide you here like Old Master did?

458
00:36:44,799 --> 00:36:46,580
That's impossible.

459
00:36:46,580 --> 00:36:47,958
Why not?

460
00:36:47,958 --> 00:36:49,459
His Lordship treats you very well.

461
00:36:49,459 --> 00:36:52,280
I can see that even if I'm dense.

462
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:55,599
Young Lady, you said that you wouldn't marry anyone before.

463
00:36:55,599 --> 00:36:58,339
But I didn't expect you would accept to be his secret lover.

464
00:36:58,339 --> 00:37:01,379
Silly, I'm not his secret lover.

465
00:37:01,379 --> 00:37:04,359
He's my secret lover instead.

466
00:37:04,359 --> 00:37:07,459
Are you saying the mighty Lord Ding is your secret lover?

467
00:37:08,400 --> 00:37:11,239
He said he agreed not to marry me,

468
00:37:11,239 --> 00:37:14,419
and he would not marry one in this life for my sake.

469
00:37:14,419 --> 00:37:19,560
He wants to stay by my side without marriage.

470
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:22,399
Obviously, he's my secret lover.

471
00:37:23,719 --> 00:37:25,478
I have to stop here. There's a grand assembly today.

472
00:37:25,478 --> 00:37:27,479
I need to leave now.

473
00:37:27,500 --> 00:37:29,700
- Put the deeds away. 
 - All right.

474
00:37:29,759 --> 00:37:30,759
I'm off.

475
00:37:51,720 --> 00:37:54,860
Why do you sulk, sweetheart?

476
00:37:55,560 --> 00:37:57,060
Here.

477
00:37:58,159 --> 00:37:59,538
Have some honey water.

478
00:37:59,538 --> 00:38:03,259
You can come to my room to check out the new jewelry.

479
00:38:05,359 --> 00:38:10,379
He doesn't care about me or look at me.

480
00:38:10,379 --> 00:38:14,239
What's the point of wearing delicate jewelry?

481
00:38:15,560 --> 00:38:19,679
My daughter is the most brilliant gem in the entire capital.

482
00:38:19,679 --> 00:38:21,819
How could he not care about you?

483
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:28,619
In his eyes, Mu Zhuohua is the gem.

484
00:38:30,359 --> 00:38:31,959
It makes sense.

485
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:34,759
She became a Tanhua at such a young age

486
00:38:34,759 --> 00:38:37,620
and stands out amongst all the ladies.

487
00:38:37,620 --> 00:38:40,719
I can only be inferior to her.

488
00:38:41,839 --> 00:38:44,680
Lord Ding is blind!

489
00:38:45,520 --> 00:38:49,560
How could a mere merchant's daughter compare to my daughter?

490
00:38:52,639 --> 00:38:53,912
A merchant's daughter?

491
00:38:53,912 --> 00:38:56,793
Do you mean Official Mu?

492
00:39:01,560 --> 00:39:04,179
Your father wanted me to keep this secret.

493
00:39:04,179 --> 00:39:07,359
But it's no harm in telling you this.

494
00:39:07,359 --> 00:39:11,879
A few days ago, he received a letter from Huaizhou, Jiangnan.

495
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:14,859
It mentions Mu Zhuohua.

496
00:39:14,859 --> 00:39:18,999
Her real name is Mu Qi, and she was born in Huaizhou.

497
00:39:19,000 --> 00:39:21,981
She's the daughter of the wealthiest merchant in Jiangnan.

498
00:39:21,981 --> 00:39:25,260
Isn't she from Yanzhou?

499
00:39:26,040 --> 00:39:29,320
She must've used some dirty ways to change her birthplace.

500
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:35,719
How could she do that?

501
00:39:35,719 --> 00:39:38,138
Are you sure, Mother?

502
00:39:38,138 --> 00:39:40,119
Could that be a mistake?

503
00:39:42,920 --> 00:39:45,339
I wouldn't lie to you.

504
00:39:46,440 --> 00:39:51,639
I saw that when I was talking to your father in the study.

505
00:39:54,539 --> 00:39:55,839
Here.

506
00:39:58,199 --> 00:39:59,899
Finish the water.

507
00:40:13,800 --> 00:40:15,600
Greetings, Your Majesty.

508
00:40:17,539 --> 00:40:22,879
Last night, you promised me you would take Miss Sun to the city tower

509
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:25,058
to see the view of the capital.

510
00:40:25,058 --> 00:40:31,100
Why did you walk away and leave her alone there?

511
00:40:37,020 --> 00:40:41,420
Your Majesty, the three princes were with her last night.

512
00:40:41,420 --> 00:40:46,239
I don't think I needed to stay there the whole time.

513
00:40:46,239 --> 00:40:49,340
I'm afraid you left for someone else.

514
00:40:49,340 --> 00:40:51,919
You wouldn't care to spend time on me.

515
00:40:51,919 --> 00:40:58,319
But I heard this person is uncouth and now has become an official.

516
00:40:58,319 --> 00:41:01,940
Now, this person is involved with Lord Ding.

517
00:41:02,719 --> 00:41:06,619
An uncouth official is harmful.

518
00:41:06,619 --> 00:41:09,499
This is a serious problem.

519
00:41:10,139 --> 00:41:14,120
Does His Majesty know about this?

520
00:41:14,120 --> 00:41:17,538
If His Majesty were to know that she's a problematic person,

521
00:41:17,538 --> 00:41:20,539
I'm afraid she'd be removed.

522
00:41:21,750 --> 00:41:25,080
Lord Ding, what are your thoughts on this?

